title: Recall Notification Report
summary: WASHINGTON, June 30, 2010 - Oregon Freeze Dry, Inc. an Albany, Ore., establishment is recalling approximately 600 pounds of Beef Stroganoff with Noodles due to a mislabeling of individual pouches that were packed with Lasagna with Meat Sauce. The products subject to recall include: 4.06-ounce...
impacted_products: 4.06-ounce pouches of "Mountain House Pro-Pak Beef Stroganoff with Noodles"
